OverHistory.CommentStrikers: Mohammad Shami TO K L Rahul
OverHistory.NewCommentry: Mohammad Shami to K L Rahul Wicket
OverHistory.Commentry: Mohammad Shami bowling to K L Rahul, good length ball, pitching outside off stump, K L Rahul plays a forward defensive shot WICKET K L Rahul c Matthew Wade b Mohammad Shami (Lucknow Super Giants 0 Runs for 1 wickets), Appeal from the fielding sidetowards Wicket Keeper
OverHistory.UPDCommentry: Mohammad Shami to K L Rahul, WICKET K L Rahul c Matthew Wade b Mohammad Shami (Lucknow Super Giants 0 Runs for 1 wicket). Mohammad Shami strikes in the first ball of the match with a PEACH of a delivery! Shami to start with the new ball for Gujarat, the Lucknow skipper on strike, starts with a good length delivery, outside off stump, nips away from the batter and gets the outside edge of Rahul's bat to Wade behind the stumps. Incredible start for Gujarat Titans!
